creator: Studio Boxcat
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to Meow Tower! Build your own tower for stray cats. 🐾

Solve Nonogram (a.k.a Picross) puzzles to buy furnitures and decorate your cats' room. Expand the tower and meet more stray cats. If you become friend with the resident cats, they might tell you a hidden story!

■ How to play:
• Solve Nonogram (a.k.a Picross) to win prizes.
• Use your prize to buy furnitures and decorate the cats' room.
• If you complete the cat's wishlist, they might tell you some juicy secret story.

■ Highlights:
• Cute and unique cats and variety of furnitures to collect.
• Hundreds of simple but challenging Nonogram puzzles.
• Reveal cats' hidden stories by completing their room.
• Full support for offline play and cloud data backup.

Want to know more about Meow Tower? Please visit us anytime.

- Nonogram enthusiasts looking for a fresh, cat-themed challenge.
